OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine and
OL,7,Fmainly light winds. Cloud increasing
OL,8,Ffrom the west overnight with outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain spreading across western and
OL,10,Fcentral areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSome early brightness in
OL,13,Fsoutheast, but generally a cloudy
OL,14,Fmorning with outbreaks of occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy rain. During the afternoon the
OL,16,Frain turns more showery and perhaps
OL,17,Fthundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
