OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers Sunday, but
OL,7,Fcloudier later. Cloud and outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain on Monday clear to sunny spells
OL,9,Fand showers. Rather cloudy Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith occasionally heavy rain or
OL,11,Fshowers.
